Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku tahu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Meski rasa takut kehilangan menghalangi kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}semua orang tetap menyongsong hari esok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tak melihat, tak peduli...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Mereka yang bahkan tak memberi kebebasan atau pun cinta,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}para malaikat dari langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Firasatku berbicara, ya, aku suka takdir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Kupasrahkan diriku, kehendakku kepada sayap ini
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:09.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tanpa lelah ku terus hidup di dunia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:13.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Jadilah pembela kebenaran meski hanya sandiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:17.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku ingin kebahagiaan tertinggi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:25.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Hanya itu saja
